    <td>
      R. de Castro, H. Pereira, R. E. Araújo, J. V. Barreras and H. C. Pangborn,
      &quot;qTSL: A Multilayer Control Framework for Managing Capacity, Temperature, Stress, and Losses in Hybrid Balancing Systems&quot;,
      IEEE Transactions on Control Systems Technology, vol. 30, no. 3, pp. 1228-1243, May 2022,
      doi: <a href=\"https://doi.org/10.1109/TCST.2021.3103483\">10.1109/TCST.2021.3103483</a>.
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td>[Hoffmann2007]</td>
    <td>
      G. M. Hoffmann, C. J. Tomlin, M. Montemerlo, and S. Thrun,
